* RAP Technical Design Document — Code Artifacts Summary
* ================================================
* Project: Sales Order Management
* RAP Type: Managed
* Draft: Yes

* CDS ENTITY LIST:
* ZI_SalesOrder      - Root Active (Table: ZSALES_ORDER)
* ZI_SalesItem       - Child Active (Table: ZSALES_ITEM)
* ZC_SalesOrder      - Root Projection (Fiori UI)
* ZC_SalesItem       - Child Projection (Fiori UI)
* ZDT_SalesOrder     - Draft table (auto-gen)

* BEHAVIOR DEFINITION (BDEF) SKELETON:
managed implementation in class ZBP_SalesOrder unique;
with draft;
define behavior for ZI_SalesOrder alias SalesOrder
persistent table zsales_order
draft table zdt_sales_order
lock master
etag master LastChangedAt
{
  create; update; delete;
  field ( readonly ) OrderId, CreatedAt, CreatedBy;
  field ( mandatory ) CustomerId, OrderDate;
  validation validateDates   on save { field OrderDate, DeliveryDate; }
  determination calcTotals   on modify { field Quantity, UnitPrice; }
  action submitOrder result [1] $self;
  association _Items { create; }
  draft action Edit; draft action Activate;
  draft action Discard; draft action Resume;
  draft determine action Prepare;
}

* SERVICE BINDING URL PATTERN:
* /sap/opu/odata4/sap/zsb_salesorder_ui/srvd/sap/zsd_salesorder/0001/
* Test: ADT > Service Binding ZSB_SALESORDER_UI > Preview

